==Most isolated major summits==
Of the 13 major summits of Hawai{{okina}}i, Mauna Kea has {{convert|3947|km|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic isolation and four peaks exceed {{convert|100|km|2|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic isolation.
