* {{cite book|title=Life in Ponds and Streams|year=1896}}
* {{cite book|title=The Out-Door World |year=1900}}
* {{cite book|title=The Sea Shore|year=1903}}
* {{cite book|title=Field and Woodland Plants|year=1909}}

